.SH CONFIGURATION FILE
The configuration file located at ~/.config/myscripts/thememgr/settings.conf supports the following settings:
.PP
.RS 4
.EX
THEMEMGR_GIT_REPO="https://github.com/thememgr"
THEMEMGR_DATA_DIR="$HOME/.local/share/themes"
THEMEMGR_FORCE_INSTALL="false"
THEMEMGR_NOTIFY_ENABLED="yes"
THEMEMGR_CLONE_DIR="$HOME/Projects/github/thememgr"
.EE
.RE
